author: Phillip Jennings
title: What's blooming this Autumn
content: The Banksia Court is full of colourful blooms this autumn with the acorn banksia (Banksia prionotes) and Banksia victoriae putting on a great show. If you look carefully you will also see some large yellow flower spikes on Banksia media, Banksia integrifolia and Banksia epica.

author: Phillip Jennings
title: Banksia Garden Upgrade
content: The Vice Chancellor has provided an innivation grant to enable us to renew the signage and provide an app for visitors to the Banksia Court garden. These improvements will be rolled out during 2019. The Murdoch University banksia garden is one of only two such gardens is this state.
